	<div style="text-align:right;">
		SOUZA, Silvia Hikari Watanabe de<sup>1</sup>; AMARAL, Andrea Novais Moreno<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
